name: XIX III XVIII V I XIII
description: The "origin" image that may well have started "Eyes of Lamia". It inspired the subsequent "Numbers" series, that were my way of dealing with emotions that I couldn't effectively process at the time. Those images helped me with expressing myself and exorcising my inner demons. They are the cornerstone of my art which is all about expression of thoughts and feelings that I fail to communicate verbally. And this image here is the root, the point of origin, even though at the time I hardly realised it.
